{"tid":1301813,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 714遊行會血流城河","createTime":"2019-07-09T17:38:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T18:09:55.000Z","uid":266309,"like":1,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e44d803604766bd416910e6f9e049ab6e6b34f92","tid":1301813,"uid":266309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T17:38:01.000Z","msg":"代朋友post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我宣布　714遊行會血流城河<br />\n因為連登仔有恩必報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家遊行前遊行期間遊行後到遊行必到地點<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">紅十字捐血站</span></span></strong><br />\n捐血救人 助人助己 <br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>原因</strong></ins><br />\n一、 6月9日，6月16日大遊行我地見到好多紅十字既急救隊幫我地 （維園外及中央圖書館外），呢幾日都一路幫我地提供心理情緒輔導 既然黎到又行過 係時候報恩 多謝下人地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n二、遊行唔多唔小影響到人 加上呢個月我地又成日遊行冇時間去捐血 希望大家都可以體現香港人精神 助人助己<br />\n<br />\n三、制造遊行形象工程 增加輿論籌碼 你見過暴徒熱心捐血未丫？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n四、大家捐下血某程度上可以幫助受傷既義士<br />\n<br />\n五、吸引外媒  捐血反送中應該全世界未試過 隨時又上曬國際頭版<br />\n<br />\n大家幫手諗個靚口號<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9v4MML8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9v4MML8.jpg&h=4516c12d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>捐血後注意事項</ins></strong><br />\n捐血後12小時內多喝飲料以補充失去的水份<br />\n捐血後12小時內避免進行劇烈運動<br />\n捐血後12小時內不宜用捐血的手提取重物或過度用力，以免影響傷口癒合<br />\n<br />\nP.S. <br />\n1. 不要阻礙遊行進度 行之前或之後去捐<br />\n2. 量力而為 我要大隻仔 健康仔<br />\n3. 身體差既巴絲留力下次捐 我擔心你既體力<br />\n4. 有冇巴絲識人 可以將個規模搞大佢<br />\n5. 一定要守秩序 唔好成事不足 因為人一定多 <br />\n6. 唔要譚詠麟再幫紅十字宣傳<br />\n7. 活動想拎光環<br />\n8. 肯定左捐血站暫時係照開 遊行可能阻到人捐 我地盡一分力 幫助社會<br />\n<br />\n大家比下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55bacb2defe6a96ba9d03cae0f1bafcad9ce20ef","tid":1301813,"uid":266309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T17:39:16.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a44a3eacfbb1690c67a5403bdee784ad96147c62","tid":1301813,"uid":266309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T17:39:46.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"144f0d43fec30dc07d1479cb3af2e643755c3040","tid":1301813,"uid":49808,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T17:41:21.000Z","msg":"無捐血好耐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無謂益9D廢老新移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5511754295d7df62b84e9084477377e008f7934","tid":1301813,"uid":215794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T17:44:52.000Z","msg":"好似聽過會運返上大陸？係咪真？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ad6ccfaea9113169bd23b2b95f2c2dc0682c6eb","tid":1301813,"uid":191776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T17:50:39.000Z","msg":"你都on9"},{"pid":"1f08bd4cb40d53fbfafb612d91bdcd44bb3ebe5b","tid":1301813,"uid":31841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T17:52:18.000Z","msg":"收皮啦,想我賣血俾支那人<br />\n當我弱智架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48c572fc36e545cb7b4835349e65e7e941e7f1fa","tid":1301813,"uid":180825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T17:52:59.000Z","msg":"捐血俾大陸人，不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ff0faff0976ba43c76464b9e5a49d948dfeef7","tid":1301813,"uid":267027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:01:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b93ba4425a9280e9c274c9fe8c2df6bb83cf4ec8","tid":1301813,"uid":26827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:09:55.000Z","msg":"食屎啦 送完錢翻去 仲要送埋血？"}]}